## RESUME DES COMMANDES

| Commande | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `devkinsta-theme-init "Nom"` | Cr√©e un th√®me Tailwind 4 |
| `devkinsta-optimize-wp` | Optimise wp-config.php |
| `npm run build` | Compile le CSS |
| `npm run dev` | Mode watch (auto-compile) |

