| RAM Total | memoryMiB | cpus | swapMiB |
|-----------|-----------|------|---------|
| 8 GB | 4096 | 4 | 2048 |
| 16 GB | 10240 | 8 | 4096 |
| 32 GB | 20480 | 16 | 4096 |

